OL,6,FAround 40 minutes later, Payne
OL,7,Fattacked a second woman on Orchard
OL,8,FStreet. He sexually assaulted her
OL,9,Fwhilst trying to open his trousers. He
OL,10,Fwas fought off by the victim, who
OL,11,Fshouted for help from two passing
OL,12,Fmembers of the public.
OL,14,FAn hour and a half later, a motorist
OL,15,Freported seeing Payne on Walter Road
OL,16,Fwith his trousers down whilst he was
OL,17,Fperforming a sexual act.
