OL,6,F"His victims fought back and thanks to
OL,7,Ftheir efforts we were able to work
OL,8,Fwith South Wales police to bring a
OL,9,Fsuccessful prosecution which will see
OL,10,FPayne spending time behind bars for
OL,11,Fhis sick crimes."
OL,13,FLeo Payne was sentenced to 11 years
OL,14,Fand three months' imprisonment which
OL,15,Fwas extended with a four years and
OL,16,Fnine months' license period on 20
OL,17,FSeptember 2024 including a requirement
OL,18,Fto register as a sex offender
OL,19,Findefinitely.
